OL,3,CMore funds to support steel workers
OL,4,Cand businesses
OL,6,FThe UK Government has announced it is
OL,7,Fdoubling funds to support workers and
OL,8,Fbusinesses affected by job losses at
OL,9,FTata Steel's Port Talbot plant.
OL,11,FMinisters said an extra #15 million
OL,12,Fwill be made available for supply
OL,13,Fchain businesses and workers affected
OL,14,Fby changes at Tata's south Wales site.
OL,16,FWelsh Secretary Jo Stevens said the
OL,17,Fmove means a fund to support
OL,18,Fbusinesses across Wales heavily
OL,19,Freliant on Tata Steel will be
OL,20,Fincreased to #30 million.
