OL,3,CMore funds to support steel workers
OL,4,Cand businesses
OL,6,FShe also announced that more
OL,7,Fbusinesses will be able to apply for
OL,8,Fthe funds and the value of individual
OL,9,Fgrants is increasing to up to #250,000
OL,10,Ffor businesses to invest in equipment,
OL,11,Fproperty, technology.
OL,13,FThe UK Government said there has been
OL,14,F"significant demand" on the existing
OL,15,Ffunding, with almost 40 businesses
OL,16,Femploying 2,000 people having begun
OL,17,Fthe application process.
OL,19,FGrants worth millions of pounds are
OL,20,Fexpected to be released in the new
OL,21,Fyear.
